    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic. This example features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, delivering 333 hp with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing aluminum control arms and a multi-link rear setup for superior kinematic control. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system recalibration and a thorough inspection of the rear subframe for stress fractures. The car exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, but the mechanical integrity is excellent, providing the linear torque curve and telepathic steering rack feedback that defines this chassis. Documented service history included.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
